        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">The unreacted ethylene oxide was assumed to leave the production process with the wastewater. This amount was calculated taken into account losses of 0.2% raw material as air emissions, and the efficiency of the reaction (95%). Further it was assumed that this wastewater is treated in an internal wastewater plant. Therefore, a removal efficiency of 90% for ethylene oxide was assumed.</comment>
